List of Sony Music Entertainment Japan artists, listed alphabetically with photos when available. This Sony Music Entertainment Japan roster includes both past and present artists. Popular Sony Music Entertainment Japan bands and artists are all listed here with information such as what genre the bands fall under and what albums they're known for. If you're looking for any of these Sony Music Entertainment Japan band's full discographies then click on their name and you can find them here on Ranker. The artists and bands on this list might be pop, rap, rock, electronic or any other genre, but what they all have in common is that they were signed by Sony Music Entertainment Japan.
